        "text": "Sellers negotiate by responding to buyer offers with counter-offers, holding firm on price when buyer demand supports it, and structuring contract terms (settlement date, conditions, inclusions) to suit their needs. Strong negotiation starts with accurate pricing and a well-run campaign that generates competition between buyers."
      }
